%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.4-ea.2/model-registry.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(Dashboard/CLI)
    participant Gateway as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Proxy as model-registry proxy<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant MySQL as MySQL Database<br/>3306/TCP TLS 1.2+
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as InferenceService Controller
    participant KServe as KServe (init container)
    participant CSI as CSI Storage Initializer
    participant ArtifactStore as Model Artifact Store
    participant CatalogSvr as Catalog Server<br/>8080/TCP
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant HF as HuggingFace API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client, MySQL: Flow 1: Model Registration via REST API
    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>HTTPS TLS
    Gateway->>Proxy: Forward request<br/>HTTP mTLS (Istio)
    Proxy->>MySQL: INSERT model metadata<br/>TLS 1.2+ Username/Password
    MySQL-->>Proxy: Result
    Proxy-->>Gateway: 201 Created
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over K8sAPI, Proxy: Flow 2: InferenceService Sync (Controller)
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch InferenceService events<br/>TLS SA Token
    Controller->>Proxy: POST/PATCH inference service state<br/>HTTP Bearer Token (optional)
    Proxy->>MySQL: Persist state
    MySQL-->>Proxy: Result
    Proxy-->>Controller: 200 OK
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update ISVC labels<br/>HTTPS TLS SA Token

    Note over KServe, ArtifactStore: Flow 3: CSI Model Download
    KServe->>CSI: Init container invocation<br/>model-registry:// URI
    CSI->>Proxy: GET model artifact location<br/>HTTP plaintext
    Proxy-->>CSI: Artifact URI
    CSI->>ArtifactStore: Download model<br/>HTTP/S3/OCI (varies)
    ArtifactStore-->>CSI: Model artifacts

    Note over CatalogSvr, HF: Flow 4: Catalog Source Sync
    CatalogSvr->>HF: Fetch model catalog<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ HF_API_KEY
    HF-->>CatalogSvr: Model metadata
    CatalogSvr->>PG: Store catalog data<br/>PostgreSQL PGUSER/PGPASSWORD
    PG-->>CatalogSvr: Result
